title: Novo Nordisk sues Hims & Hers over copycat versions of Wegovy drugs; Hims stock falls 18%
summary_full: Novo is asking the court to permanently ban Hims from selling compounded versions of its drugs that infringe patents, and is seeking to recover damages.
summary_public: Novo is asking the court to permanently ban Hims from selling compounded versions of its drugs that infringe patents, and is seeking to recover damages.
